name: unComo
overview:
UnComo.com is a newly created company, by the web that has the vocation to help people find practical solutions to problems or challenges of everyday.

Young and dynamic company with great potential for relatively rapid growth and is starting to have a significant market share.

UnComo.com staffed with people with more than 10 years of experience in the Internet world and with young workers eager to learn and grow.

To continue to grow, we are using the best techniques of positioning on the Internet, by creating quality content, a very good technical base, a very good design of the web, etc..
